title: CF-StraightStudFuckfest
description:
With Cade and Dawson teamed up on one side and Ryan and Brent teammates on the other, things were ready to get rolling. The game got going, with Lucas playing quarterback and Logan keeping store, and everyone had a blast. It was great seeing the guys have fun, get some sun, sweat all over and go at it on the field. Cade, Dawson, Brent and Ryan are already quite a competitive bunch, and with the winners getting topping honors and the losers set to get drilled up the ass, things were that much more competitive and intense. All the while, however, the guys were also just having a blast and tons of fun. Even with the high stakes, everyone was in a good mood and surprisingly relaxed!
